::Prowl::

An exciting feeling runs through Prowl, going from his head down to his legs 
as Iron Raptor rubs him on his neck and lets our a breath. He smiles.

"That's good to hear," he says a bit quetly, leaning forward and kissing Iron 
Raptor, his hands once again closing around her. One of his hands slides down 
her back, pressing her waist closer against his. His spark was spinning at 
very high rates, speeding up his mechfluid and rising his level of excitement.

He leans away as a thought occurs to him, looking at the door. "Computer, 
lock door," he says so that the computer could hear his voice. There was a 
'whoosh' as the door magnetically sealed itself, leaving the two lovers with 
their privacy.

Prowl turns back to Iron Raptor, his hand resuming its position on her thigh, 
once again pulling her to him. He looks at her optics, love showing clearly 
in his own as he kisses her again, the hand on her thigh sliding down ever 
farther...
